  "detailed_description": "Delve deep through the dark corners of the soul, and  descend into - the Mantle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568210/extras/cf5d80fb2f68d95b371d08c579cb0e66.poster.avif?t=1636110408\" width=668 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568210/extras/cf5d80fb2f68d95b371d08c579cb0e66.webm?t=1636110408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568210/extras/cf5d80fb2f68d95b371d08c579cb0e66.mp4?t=1636110408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>\"What is this place? <br><br>What is wrong with me? <br><br>I might need help\"<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568210/extras/50e09458c2f9f06c53b198edabd6726c.poster.avif?t=1636110408\" width=776 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568210/extras/50e09458c2f9f06c53b198edabd6726c.webm?t=1636110408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568210/extras/50e09458c2f9f06c53b198edabd6726c.mp4?t=1636110408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Mantle is an Emotional Platformer set beneath the crust of the Earth. <br>Falling deep into the pit of despair: Can you overcome this inner turmoil?<br><br>Make use of your Guiding Light , and traverse a variety of precarious subterranean environments.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568210/extras/faff40730acd0ed19727df2250c1a5b1.poster.avif?t=1636110408\" width=656 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568210/extras/faff40730acd0ed19727df2250c1a5b1.webm?t=1636110408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568210/extras/faff40730acd0ed19727df2250c1a5b1.mp4?t=1636110408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Key Features<br>- This is a journey of self reflection and understanding<br>- Precise platforming will challenge your dexterity <br>- Soundtrack designed to soothe, immerse and uplift<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568210/extras/b68d09c50fc69023dbf20a09f22d689e.poster.avif?t=1636110408\" width=654 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568210/extras/b68d09c50fc69023dbf20a09f22d689e.webm?t=1636110408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1568210/extras/b68d09c50fc69023dbf20a09f22d689e.mp4?t=1636110408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
